          "patch_url": "https://github.com/mochajs/mocha/pull/5544.patch",
          "merged_at": null
        },
        "body": "fixes #5532 \r\n\r\n## Summary\r\nFixes the regression where command-line `--reporter-options` parameter doesn't override [.mocharc.yml](cci:7://file:///Users/sohamsaranga/Desktop/mocha%20pr%20t/.mocharc.yml:0:0-0:0) settings. This issue was introduced in v8.3.0.\r\n\r\n## Changes Made\r\n- **Modified [lib/cli/options.js](cci:7://file:///Users/sohamsaranga/Desktop/mocha%20pr%20t/mocha/lib/cli/options.js:0:0-0:0)**: \r\n  - Moved command-line args to the end of config objects list for higher priority\r\n  - Added special handling for `reporter-option` to detect CLI usage and override config file values\r\n- **Added comprehensive tests** in [test/cli/options-reporter-option-override.spec.js](cci:7://file:///Users/sohamsaranga/Desktop/mocha%20pr%20t/mocha/test/cli/options-reporter-option-override.spec.js:0:0-0:0)\r\n\r\n## Test Coverage\r\nThe fix handles all scenarios:\r\n- CLI options override config file\r\n- Both `--reporter-options` and `--reporter-option` aliases work\r\n- Both space-separated and `=` syntax work  \r\n- Multiple CLI options use the last one\r\n- Config file options work when no CLI is provided\r\n\r\n## Verification\r\n```bash\r\n# Test with config file having: reporter-options: ['output=./test-reports/xunit.xml']\r\nmocha --reporter-options output=./test-reports/cli.xml\r\n# Should create cli.xml, not xunit.xml",
